tool_description: Follow all volleyball live games and results on VolleyballAPI. Covering all major leagues and tournaments (from national and international leagues to world championships for both men and women) VolleyballAPI offers information in real-time. For more detailed information about the most popular leagues check Brazilian Volleyball Super League (men), Brazilian Volleyball Super League (women), CEV Champions League, FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League and FIVB Volleyball Men's Nations League.
name: VolleyballAPI
title: VolleyballAPI

api_list.name: MatchHead2Head
api_list.description: Get headtohead matches by custom ID

required_parameters.name: customId
required_parameters.description: The custom ID of the match you want to retrieve the head-to-head matches for. It is obtained from the match.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://volleyballapi.p.rapidapi.com/api/volleyball/match/oCpswQIb/h2h"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "volleyballapi.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
